omWeb?topicID=299.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: My Scamming Experiment</span><hr size=1> You purported to be carrying out a an experiment, was a valid and laudible aim.  What you should have done is handed each item gained back to the person concerned, with a gentle chiding for exposing themselves to risk, advice not to do it again, and perhap 100pp to thank them for their misplaced trust and time.<br><br>What you actually did was torment and harrass and upset people for no valid reason whatsoever.  Scamming for personal gain is objectionable, but setting out to deliberately inflict distress and alarm is contemptable.<br><br>Ysall the Kind<br>58 Enchanter <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/bemarr.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=ysallkind>YsallKind</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 87<br> <font color=#E9D756>(12/20/01 2:03:34 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrscammeralert.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=299.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: My Scamming Experiment</span><hr size=1> Oh, and thank you for putting up your real name, so you can go on our do not group, do not port, do not rez, and do not guild lists.<br><br>Ysall the Kind <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#575757><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/uhoppkins.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hoppkins</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 187<br> <font color=#E9D756>(12/20/01 2:49:19 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrscammeralert.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=299.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: My Scamming Experiment</span><hr s